            "title": "Western Red Cedar",
            "text": "<ul><li><strong>Durability:</strong> This wood is naturally resistant to decay and insects, ensuring a long-lasting fence that demands minimal maintenance.</li><li><strong>Lightweight:</strong> Western Red Cedar's relatively lightweight nature makes it an installer-friendly choice, reducing the effort and time required for fence installation and repairs.</li><li><strong>Aromatic Delight:</strong> Enjoy the pleasant, natural aroma of Western Red Cedar, enhancing the ambiance of your outdoor space.</li><li><strong>Sustainability:</strong> Western Red Cedar is sourced from responsibly managed forests, making it an eco-conscious choice for environmentally aware consumers.</li><li><strong>Natural Beauty</strong>: Western Red Cedar boasts a stunning natural grain pattern and rich reddish-brown color that adds an elegant and timeless aesthetic to any outdoor setting.</li><li><strong>Weather Resistance</strong>: This wood's inherent weather-resistant properties help it withstand the harshest of climates, ensuring your fence remains strong and attractive for years to come.</li></ul>",
            "align": "left",
            "width": "1/2"
          }
        }
