          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Michigan White Cedar",
            "text": "<ul><li><strong>Native Beauty:</strong> Michigan White Cedar boasts a natural, pale appearance that lends a timeless charm to any outdoor space.</li><li><strong>Exceptional Resilience:</strong> This wood is naturally resistant to rot, decay, and insects, ensuring your fence stands strong against the elements.</li><li><strong>Local Sustainability:</strong> By choosing Michigan White Cedar, you're supporting sustainable forestry practices and reducing your environmental footprint.</li><li><strong>Low Maintenance:</strong> Enjoy a low-maintenance fencing solution that retains its beauty with minimal effort.</li><li><strong>Time and Cost Savings</strong>: With its low maintenance requirements, Michigan White Cedar allows you to spend more time enjoying your outdoor space and less time on upkeep, saving you both time and money.</li><li><strong>Versatile Application</strong>: Michigan White Cedar can be easily adapted to various fence styles and landscaping designs, allowing you to create a customized and harmonious outdoor environment.</li><li>Enhanced Property Aesthetics: A Michigan White Cedar fence not only enhances the value of your property but also brings a touch of Michigan's natural beauty to your outdoor living space, creating a welcoming and picturesque atmosphere.</li></ul>",
            "align": "left",
            "width": "1/2"
          }
        }
